query:
SELECT 
  u.id,
  u.name,
  u.email,
  u.role,
  u.tipoUsuarioId,
  t.nome as tipo_nome,
  u.status
FROM users u
LEFT JOIN tipos_usuario t ON u.tipoUsuarioId = t.id
WHERE u.status = 'aprovado'
ORDER BY u.id DESC
LIMIT 15
